                >
                  <li>
                    Led a team of 5 developers in the creation of a new
                    e-commerce platform, resulting in a 20% increase in sales.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    Architected and implemented a scalable frontend using React
                    and TypeScript.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    Improved application performance by 30% through code
                    optimization and lazy loading.
